Package emissary.parser

Class SimpleNioParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • emissary.parser.SessionParser
      • emissary.parser.NIOSessionParser
        • emissary.parser.SimpleNioParser
  • public class SimpleNioParser
extends NIOSessionParser
    A very simple minded parser implementation that assumes each input channel is one session. This parser has no idea about headers and footers, just the basic session and not much of an idea about that.
